{"tid":2014373,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國歌法除左嚴捉改歌詞及歪曲貶損 更提強制教育中小學國歌歷史","createTime":"2020-05-13T04:01:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T05:27:05.000Z","uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"03d8c93b7acee784e76f1c21c531ddd7b96ed1f4","tid":2014373,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T04:01:49.000Z","msg":"全國人大常委會去年底通過將《國歌法》納入香港《基本法》附件三，並交由特區政府透過本地立法實施。政制及內地事務局昨向立法會提交的文件披露，當局草擬《國歌條例草案》的建議內容中，訂明應由特首規定奏唱國歌的場合，列明奏唱時出席者須肅立莊重，中小學生須學唱及了解國歌歷史，禁止改歌詞及歪曲貶損等行為，違法者可被罰款5萬元及監禁3年。政府建議條文中指出，草案將於立法通過後生效，政府消息人士表明，條例不會有追溯期。"},{"pid":"47302f3c65ae040ba1bf43297dc064080313e3ef","tid":2014373,"uid":49392,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T04:03:09.000Z","msg":"作詞人田漢下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17b42898a0ee5b6473779671ac6ba60f4a165aea","tid":2014373,"uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T04:03:49.000Z","msg":"有冇人敢教呀?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/_V2fVC2Oi_Oz1mTzHnmsL0Ykz5FtyLWhWP1Ju7IacBtHjbbfs2XMZcxJWT42Ti4jPdZkirYc7MKOyiX_3q790fpbPj-0cqiy0adut-L9wocelb5cqLaXFkZyEsa3yaJe1cg1ngNBCGMYvy5wJ3mXRweJ2Q_IenvZiv1l2tZb-4g\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Fproxy%2F_V2fVC2Oi_Oz1mTzHnmsL0Ykz5FtyLWhWP1Ju7IacBtHjbbfs2XMZcxJWT42Ti4jPdZkirYc7MKOyiX_3q790fpbPj-0cqiy0adut-L9wocelb5cqLaXFkZyEsa3yaJe1cg1ngNBCGMYvy5wJ3mXRweJ2Q_IenvZiv1l2tZb-4g&h=aa4146e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8cc165bcfc5e57061d2cf780f1d762d4379950c","tid":2014373,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T04:03:55.000Z","msg":"好似作首歌個人最後係批鬥死???<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e65ff69295601394151a3de3f61ea118dcdcd7e","tid":2014373,"uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T04:04:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.pentoy.hk/wp-content/uploads/